DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
985::$$$message_0005_0000_0000$$$::The stuff from this morning is unfinished.[lr]::
986::$$$message_0005_0000_0001$$$::So I should at least finish what I started.::
987::$$$message_0005_0001_0000$$$::"Change of plans. You want me to finish what we started in the morning, right? Leave it to me. I'll finish all repairs before exams start."[lr]::
988::$$$message_0005_0001_0001$$$::"That'll be helpful. Let's go check on our patient in the art club."[lr]::
989::$$$message_0005_0001_0002$$$::"Sure thing. Oh, but make sure there's nobody around. I can't concentrate when there's people around."[lr]::
990::$$$message_0005_0001_0003$$$::"Of course. I won't let anyone get in your way."[lr]::
991::$$$message_0005_0001_0004$$$::Keeping up with Issei's brisk pace, I follow him out of the classroom.::
992::$$$message_0005_0002_0000$$$::The sun has long since set by the time we step outside the building.[lr]::
993::$$$message_0005_0002_0001$$$::The school gate is already closed.[lr]::
994::$$$message_0005_0002_0002$$$::It's seven o'clock, way past the time they close the gates. But thanks to Issei's help, the two of us avoided trouble.::
995::$$$message_0005_0003_0000$$$::"You really helped me out today. I'll repay you for this, so don't hesitate to ask me if anything comes up."[lr]::
996::$$$message_0005_0003_0001$$$::"Sure. I don't think anything will come up, though."[lr]::
997::$$$message_0005_0003_0002$$$::I didn't help him because I wanted something in return, and I don't think I would ask Issei for anything impossible.::
998::$$$message_0005_0004_0000$$$::"Honestly, you might have to reconsider being such a good guy all the time. Having you around is certainly helpful, but I can't stand when other people use you for their own ends. Helping people may be a good thing, but you should be more selective about who you help. You just do everything everyone asks."[lr]::
999::$$$message_0005_0004_0001$$$::"You think so? Am I really that much of a pushover?"[lr]::
1000::$$$message_0005_0004_0002$$$::"Mmhm. And that means heartless idiots are going to use you as they wish. You're a busy man, so it wouldn't hurt for you to decline requests from time to time."::
1001::$$$message_0005_0005_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
1002::$$$message_0005_0005_0001$$$::I honestly can't tell, but I think Issei is concerned for me.[lr]::
1003::$$$message_0005_0005_0002$$$::Ever since middle school, I've always been told how helpful I am since I never decline requests or ask anything in return.::
1004::$$$message_0005_0006_0000$$$::I guess Issei thinks that's unhealthy.[lr]::
1005::$$$message_0005_0006_0001$$$::But I'm only doing this because I want to, and I decline any requests I feel are impossible, so there's no issue.::
1006::$$$message_0005_0007_0000$$$::"You really don't need to worry about this. I know myself and my limits. Besides, helping people [font italic=true]is[font italic=false] a good thing, and not the sort of thing the son of a temple should be telling anyone [font italic=true]not[font italic=false] to do."[lr]::
1007::$$$message_0005_0007_0001$$$::"But you take to it an extreme. You're going to burn yourself out."::
1008::$$$message_0005_0008_0000$$$::"I'll keep your warning in mind. See you tomorrow at school."[lr]::
1009::$$$message_0005_0008_0001$$$::"Mmm-hm. See you tomorrow."::
1010::$$$message_0005_0009_0000$$$::Issei leaves, looking dissatisfied.[lr]::
1011::$$$message_0005_0009_0001$$$::Issei lives in Ryudou Temple, located on top of a mountain. Which means he and I have to go our separate ways.::

